fullplot: "Case 39" centers on an idealistic social worker who saves an abused 10-year-old girl from her parents only to discover that the girl is not as innocent as she thinks.
plot: A social worker fights to save a girl from her abusive parents, only to discover that the situation is more dangerous than she ever expected.
title: Case 39

tomatoes.consensus: Director Christian Alvert has a certain stylish flair, but it's wasted on Case 39's frightless, unoriginal plot.
